    "But the Nethinims dwelt in Ophel: and Ziha and Gispa were over the Nethinims.",
    "The overseer also of the Levites at <span class=\"place\">Jerusalem</span> was Uzzi the son of Bani, the son of Hashabiah, the son of Mattaniah, the son of Micha. Of the sons of Asaph, the singers were over the business of the house of God.",
